s: I've tried the three brands of Low/No Waste seed I've found readily available: Audubon Park, Kaytee, and Pour Joy. Before trying the others, I used probably a dozen bags of Audubon, both purchased locally and on Amazon. I've found the quality to be hit or miss - mostly miss, between bags.
